Task: Implement Update Customer Command with Validation

Define UpdateCustomerCommand

Create an UpdateCustomerCommand class that inherits from IRequest.
Include all properties from the Customer class.
Inside this class, define an inner handler class that inherits from IRequestHandler<UpdateCustomerCommand>.
Inject INorthwindDbContext and IMapper into the handler's constructor.
In the Handle method, retrieve the customer from the database, update its properties, and persist the changes.
Define UpdateCustomerCommandValidator

Create an UpdateCustomerCommandValidator class that inherits from AbstractValidator<UpdateCustomerCommand>.
Add validation rules for all properties in the constructor.
